      Obviously on the run
   =20
 =20

A major difference between the traditional financial industry and the crypt=
o financial industry is that the people who run multibillion-dollar compani=
es in traditional finance tend to be (1) in their 40s or older and (2) advi=
sed by lots of lawyers and public-relations professionals, while the people=
 who run multibillion-dollar companies in crypto tend to be (1) like 23 and=
 (2) tweeting constantly=C2=A0from their own phones with no outside guidanc=
e. Imagine the chief executive officer of a traditional finance firm who va=
porized=C2=A0tens of billions of dollars of customer money and was investig=
ated by police. What would he do? He=E2=80=99d shut up and have his lawyers=
 put out anodyne statements about how he looked forward to clearing his nam=
e. Would he flee the country? Possibly! Would he tweet about it? Probably n=
ot.
Do Kwon is   a breath of fresh air in that sense:

Do Kwon, the founder of the collapsed Luna and TerraUSD tokens, said he=E2=
=80=99s not =E2=80=9Con the run=E2=80=9D hours after Singapore police state=
d he was no longer in the country.=C2=A0 =E2=80=A6
Korean prosecutors refuted his comments on Sunday and alleged Do Kwon is =
=E2=80=9Cobviously on the run,=E2=80=9D according to Yonhap News Agency. He=
 had plans to flee the country before the collapse of the Luna token in May=
, the report said. Prosecutors said Kwon is not cooperating with probes and=
 he told investigators via an attorney he had no intention to appear before=
 them for questioning, Yonhap said, citing people it didn=E2=80=99t identif=
y.=C2=A0

To be fair, a few minutes after tweeting =E2=80=9CI am not =E2=80=98on the =
run=E2=80=99 or anything similar,=E2=80=9D  Kwon also tweeted =E2=80=9CTbh =
havent gone running in a while, need to cut some calories,=E2=80=9D which I=
 suppose is a winking way to say okay, fine, actually I am on the run. Sout=
h Korea has   asked Interpol for help catching him. I will be following the=
 chase with interest, possibly on Kwon=E2=80=99s Twitter account.

