 advertises =E2=80=9Cno slippage=E2=80=9D</a>: =E2=80=9CEnter and exit posi=
tions with minimal spread and zero price impact,=E2=80=9D <a href=3D"https:=
//link.mail.bloombergbusiness.com/click/29099936.278538/aHR0cHM6Ly9nbXguaW8=
